Cell["\<\
Therefore 
if v=1 (mod 4) ---> Psi2 (r) != t^2 (mod 4)  -- -> Cond 3 ---> II
f v=3 (mod 4) ---> Psi2 (r) = t^2 (mod 4)  -- -> No Cond 3 ---> III\
