Cell["\<\
Therefore
if u=1(mod 4) --->  Psi2 (r) != t^2 (mod 4)  -- -> Cond 3 ---> II
if u=3(mod 4) --->  Psi2 (r) = t^2 (mod 4)  -- -> NO Cond 3 ---> IV
\
\>", "Text",
