Cell["\<\
if u=1(mod 4)---> Psi2 (r) != t^2 (mod 16)  =====>  Condition 6 --> I0^*
if u=3(mod 4)---> Psi2 (r) = 2^2 (mod 16)  =====>  NO Condition 6 --> IV^*\
\>", "Text",
